P
\mathbb{C}
(0,0)
|P(z)| \geq |a_n z^n| - |a_{n-1}z^{n-1}+ \cdots +a_1z+a_0|.
P(z)= \sum_{i = 0}^n a_i z^i
|z| > 1
 |u - v| \geqslant |u| - |v|. 
 |u| = |(u - v) + v| \leqslant |u - v| + |v|. 
u = a_nz^n
v = - \left( a_{n-1} z^{n-1} + \cdots + a_1 z + a_0 \right)
|-v| = |v|
|x| = |x -y + y|\leq |x-y| + |y|
|x| - |y| \leq |x-y|
x = a_n z^n
y = -(a_0 + \cdots + a_{n-1} z^{n-1})
